### 5. Backend — Core Services

#### [NEW] [server/src/services/serverConfig.service.ts](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/server/src/services/serverConfig.service.ts)

Generates server configuration files based on `ServerType`:

- **Caddy**: Caddyfile block with subdomain → directory/port mapping
- **Nginx**: Server block with `server_name`, `root`/`proxy_pass`, `location` directives
- **Apache**: VirtualHost with `ServerName`, `DocumentRoot`/`ProxyPass`
- **Static**: Caddy/Nginx file-server config pointing at the directory

Each generator also supports custom domains — when a custom domain is added, the config includes both `subdomain.runnable.dev` and the custom domain in the server names.

#### [NEW] [server/src/services/process.service.ts](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/server/src/services/process.service.ts)

- Spawns and manages child processes for each project's server
- Tracks PIDs, logs stdout/stderr to rotating log files
- Provides [start()](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/client/src/api/projects.ts#43-45), [stop()](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/client/src/api/projects.ts#45-46), [restart()](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/client/src/api/projects.ts#46-47), [status()](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/client/src/api/projects.ts#47-48), [getLogs()](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/server/src/services/process.service.ts#101-115)
- Emits status changes via Socket.IO

